name: FMovieSceneTrackEvalOptions
doc: Generic evaluation options for any track

bEvalNearestSection: When evaluating empty space on a track, will evaluate the last position of the previous section (if possible), or the first position of the next section, in that order of preference.
bEvaluateInPreroll: Evaluate this track as part of its parent sub-section's pre-roll, if applicable
bEvaluateInPostroll: Evaluate this track as part of its parent sub-section's post-roll, if applicable
